Class ComplexPolynomial

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.fractals.complex.ComplexPolynomial

  • public final class ComplexPolynomial
extends Object
    ComplexPolynomial represents a polynomial which factors are Complex. Class instances are immutable.

    Luka Skugor

    • Constructor Detail

      • ComplexPolynomial

        public ComplexPolynomial(Complex... factors)
        Creates a new polynomial with given factors. Factors are given from those which stand to variables with higher power. For example for polynomial 2*x^2 + 3*x + 1 given factors should be 2, 3, 1.
        Parameters:
        factors - polynomial's factors
